    <span class="bookmark hide"><a class="url entry-title" href="phillyburbs.com/news/local/burlington_county_times_news/hot-chocolate-candy-s-sweetness-in-a-mug/article_a0f99c49-ce9e-5ee0-adcc-5f2229ab8c52.html" rel="bookmark">Hot chocolate: Candy's sweetness in a mug</a></span>

        
                <!-- AP Byline -->
                
                    <span class="author vcard"><span class="fn">By Peg QuannStaff writer</span></span> 
                
                    
                        <span class="hide source-org vcard"><span class="org fn">PhillyBurbs.com</span></span>
                    
            
